he temperature of the Universe to the Planck value\n$T_P=10^{32}$ K, which may be seen as the \"Big Bang\" producing $4 \\cdot\n10^{30}$ GW of power.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 May 2014 15:59:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 May 2014 13:00:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 23 May 2014 01:40:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-05-26"}
